WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.500
The settings learners can adjust include:

00:00:03.150 --> 00:00:06.200
selecting dark or light mode training options,

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:14.200
customizable captions settings
such as language, color, and size,

00:00:16.150 --> 00:00:22.000
adjustable playback speed for all videos
from 0.5 times the speed

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:24.150
to two times the speed,

00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:32.200
enabling or disabling the transcript
when viewing video content.